Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:02.72,Haiyore-main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,{Oh, by the way, there's a \Npackage for you, Nyaruko-san}À đúng rồi, con có bưu kiện đó Nyaruko-san.
